text: Jangy-Jol (or Dzhangi-Dzhol) may refer to the following places in Kyrgyzstan: *Jangy-Jol, Chuy, a village in Chuy District, Chuy Region *Jangy-Jol, Kemin, a village in Kemin District, Chuy Region *Jangy-Jol, Aksy, a village in Aksy District, Jalal-Abad Region *Jangy-Jol, Toktogul, a village in Toktogul District, Jalal-Abad Region *Jangy-Jol, Naryn, a village in Kochkor District, Naryn Region *Jangy-Jol, Aravan, a village in Aravan District, Osh Region *Jangy-Jol, Uzgen, a village in Uzgen District, Osh Region
title: Jangy-Jol
